<h3>Information</h3>
<div class="paddedcontent">These sites have <em>referred</em> a visitor to your site.  This means that they have created a link to your site, and visitors have used that link.</div>
<div class="paddedcontent">The list on this page is not the same as the one on the <a href="linksin">Sites linking in</a> page.  For an entry to appear on this list, the referring page must have featured a link to your site at some point during the period covered by these stats, but may no longer have the link.  The link must also have been followed by at least one user, otherwise the site logs would not be aware of the link.</div>